content: The mentorship program is expanding. More seasoned developers are stepping up to guide the newcomers.
Began interviewing artists for the AI ethics paper. Their insights are invaluable for our research.
AI ethics for creative processes is more complex than I thought. But the journey is as enlightening as the destination.
The tech retreat logistics are coming together. It's not just about coding; it's about community building.
Just had a virtual meet-up with some of the conference speakers. The lineup is shaping up to be quite impressive.
